Rizwan Ahmed -LRB- -LSB- ; born 1 December 1982 -RRB- , also known as Riz MC , is a British actor and rapper of Pakistani descent .
As an actor , he was initially known for his work in independent films such as The Road to Guantanamo , Shifty , Four Lions , Trishna , and Ill Manors , before his breakout role in Nightcrawler .
Since then , he has appeared in the films Una , Jason Bourne , and the first Star Wars Anthology film , Rogue One .
He also starred in the HBO miniseries The Night Of as Nasir Khan ; the show and his performance were critically lauded , earning him Golden Globe and SAG nominations .
He appeared on TIME magazine 's The Most Influential People of 2017 list .
As a rapper , he is a member of the Swet Shop Boys .